ramme Associate roles in our London and Manchester offices. The roles start in December and the deadline to apply is Friday 26 September.</div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.7272720336914px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.7272720336914px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">If you would like to apply, or have any questions, please contact the relevant person via the email address on the role descriptions.</div><div><br></div><p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; margin-bottom: 12pt;"><font size="2"><br></font></p>]]></td>
